				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody"><span style="font-weight: bold">Servant of Marr pet heal HP test:</span>
<br />

<br />
(method as in <a href="http://forum.magecompendium.com/tower/viewtopic.php?t=3145" target="_blank" class="postlink">here</a>)
<br />

<br />

<br />
<span style="font-style: italic">Four tests:</span>
<br />

<br />
11% - Pet starting HP
<br />
47% - Planar Renewal (36%)
<br />
84% - Planar Renewal (37%)
<br />

<br />
7% - Pet starting HP
<br />
43% - Planar Renewal (36%)
<br />
79% - Planar Renewal (36%)
<br />

<br />
20% - Pet starting HP
<br />
56% - Planar Renewal (36%)
<br />
93% - Planar Renewal (37%)
<br />

<br />
9% - Pet starting HP
<br />
74% - Mend Companion (65%)
<br />

<br />

<br />
<span style="font-style: italic">Results:</span>
<br />

<br />
Mean heal = 36.33..%
<br />
<span style="font-weight: bold">Servant of Marr</span> (<span style="text-decoration: underline">unfocused</span>) <span style="font-weight: bold">total HP</span> = 1200 / 0.3633.. = <span style="font-weight: bold">3303 HP</span>
<br />

<br />

<br />
<span style="font-style: italic">Confirmation:</span>
<br />

<br />
Mend Companion = 65%
<br />
<span style="font-weight: bold">Servant of Marr</span> (<span style="text-decoration: underline">unfocused</span>) <span style="font-weight: bold">total HP</span> = <a href="http://lucy.fnord.net/spell.html?id=2752&source=Live" target="_blank" class="postlink">2146</a> / 0.65 = <span style="font-weight: bold">3302 HP</span><br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=86775&resize=true" target="_new">Magelo</a></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
			</tr>
		</table></td>
