				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Testing method: Just counted the damage a mob did to the pet before the pet died. Ran several tests with each pet to get more accurate results. No buffs or focus items were used.
<br />

<br />
Lvl 4: Max hit 12
<br />
Air hp: 75
<br />
Earth hp: 95
<br />
Fire hp: 50
<br />
Water hp: 80
<br />

<br />
Lvl 8: Max hit <span style="font-weight: bold">16</span>
<br />
Air hp: 175
<br />
Earth hp: 250
<br />
Fire hp: 125
<br />
Water hp: 200
<br />

