				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">ElementalMasteryBlast (proc)
<br />
1:  Decrease Hitpoints by 47 (L1) to 175 (L65) (143 for standard epic pet)
<br />

<br />
ElementalMasteryStrike (stun, recast time 12 seconds)
<br />
1:  Stun(3.00 sec/6000) 
<br />
2:  Decrease Hitpoints by 36 (L1) to 100 (L65)  (84 for standard epic pet)
<br />

<br />
Pets do regen while fighting. However it is substantially lower than their non-aggro regen.
<br />

<br />
Proof: Pull out a high regen pet (such as PoP pets), have them get beat down, and during the fight DoT them with a weak DoT (10 or 20hp/tic max). During the fight their HP will rise.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
			</tr>
